<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a17Aug1937"><font color="red">17 August 1937</font> <i>NLGC</i> (from G. Griffin to Paul L&eacute;on): Thanks very much for your letter which I have only received. I am returning the copy of D&apos;Annunzio autographed for Mr Joyce. I am also returning in the same parcel the proofs of &ldquo;The Mime of Nick Mick and the Maggies&rdquo;. I am keeping the copy of the Convegio for just two days more. </div>
